sequenceDiagram
  participant CLI as CLI
  participant RT as Runtime Facade
  participant ST as Conversation State
  participant PR as Provider Adapter
  participant LLM as Real LLM
  participant EB as Event Bus

  CLI->>RT: run("テストの失敗を修正する")
  RT->>EB: UserMessage event
  RT->>ST: build model request
  ST-->>RT: messages + visible tools
  RT->>PR: stream(ModelRequest)
  PR->>LLM: provider-specific API call
  LLM-->>PR: raw stream chunks
  PR-->>RT: ModelEvent stream
  RT->>EB: append ModelEvent
  RT-->>CLI: render text delta
